      "side": 1,
      "message": "I had a similar reasoning while writing this method: if I was\nto call it e.g. SSDLessThan16GB() then it might attract other\nusers, but the implementation as it is only includes a few\nmodels where we know the PlatformEncoding test fails due to\nthe SSD being (always) too small. (More below).",
