      "writtenOn": "2021-03-16T02:09:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Since https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id\u003d1186743 is getting some traction, I am in favor of leaving the hardcoded lists in the tests as-is for now and adding this method to actually depend on size.  Then it can be SSDLessThan16GB() instead.\n\nEvery other condition in this file has a definition that is based on hardware, and I don\u0027t like the idea of adding one for \"doesn\u0027t work on this subset of tests\" without there also being a reason based on hardware.",
      "parentUuid": "c71e2e91_76343099",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 528,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 528,
        "endChar": 40
