      "writtenOn": "2021-03-03T00:00:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Long term it seems better to add a field to the device config rather than manually id boards.  Can\u0027t platforms can have different skus with different sizes or types of drives?  I suspect it cannot be done now until more work is done with HWID data, but it\u0027s worth looking into.  See crbug.com/1070299",
